results.text: Assuming that A user has never enrolled
And they have completed Form 1
Given the user is on form 2
When a blank form is submitted
Then should redirect to the form 2 page
And should say card holder's name required
And should say card number is required
And should say expiration month is required
And should say expiration year is required
Given the user is on form 2
When the visa card number is too short
And the user clicks View Scores
Then should say credit card number too short
And should stay on Form 2
Given the user is on form 2
When the american express card number is invalid
And the user clicks View Scores
Then should say credit card number too short
And should stay on Form 2
Given the user is on form 2
When the card number is random letters
And the user clicks View Scores
Then should say credit card number too short
And should stay on Form 2
Given the user is on form 2
When all fields are entered
And the page is submitted
Then should redirect to the thank you page
And the customer id should show
